        "answer_count": 3,
        "title": "Split a String by another string",
        "body": "<p>I'm wondering about how I can do something like this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] emoticon;\nemoticon=e.split(\":)\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Is it possible to be done with split(); or is there another way around?<\/p>\n",
